                 <div class="statement__text">&quot;If you actually took the number of Muslims [sic] Americans, we'd be one of the largest Muslim countries in the world.&quot;</div>
                 <p class="statement__meta">&mdash; <a href="/personalities/barack-obama/">Barack Obama</a> on Monday, June 1st, 2009 in interview with Canal Plus Television</p>
