 <a href="http://www.whitehouse.gov/the_press_office/Transcript-of-the-Interview-of-the-President-by-Laura-Haim-Canal-Plus-6-1-09/" target="_blank">
  Interview with Canal Plus
 </a>
 , accessed June 4, 2009
</p>
<p>
 U.S. Census Bureau,
 <a href="http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/GCTTable?_bm=y&amp;-geo_id=01000US&amp;-_box_head_nbr=GCT-T1-R&amp;-ds_name=PEP_2008_EST&amp;-_lang=en&amp;-format=US-40S&amp;-_sse=on" target="_blank">
  California's population
 </a>
 , accessed June 4, 2009
</p>
<p>
 <a href="https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/index.html" target="_blank">
  CIA Online World Factbook
 </a>
 , accessed June 4, 2009
</p>
<p>
 NationMaster,
 <a href="http://www.nationmaster.com/country/us-united-states/rel-religion" target="_blank">
  number and percentage of Muslims living in the United States
 </a>
 , accessed June 4, 2009
</p>
<p>
 National Public Radio,
 <a href="http://www.npr.org/blogs/thetwo-way/2009/06/us_is_one_of_the_largest_musli.html" target="_blank">
  U.S. Is One of 'Largest Muslim Countries'? Not Really, Mr. President
 </a>
 , by Mark Memmott, June 3, 2009
</p>
<p>
 Islamic Information Center,
 <a href="http://www.islamicinformationcenter.org/interfaith-center/interfaith-center/census-statistics-for-muslims-in-america.html" target="_blank">
  estimate of Muslims living in the United States
 </a>
 , accessed June 4, 2009
